~ start
Welcome to the hospital! Today marks your first day as a nurse practitioner.
The earthquake 2 days ago caused a ton of injuries, so hospitals are working nonstop to help as many patients as they can as quickly as possible.
Use your SOAP notes to learn about your patient. SOAP notes are used by real healthcare providers, providing structure to organize notes into Subjective, Objective, Assessment and Plan.
The Subjective and Objective sections will be most useful to you here, as the Assessment and Plan are up to you to make. After you read, peek at your manual to find the best tool to use and how to use it.
Try to use your tools correctly and quickly, and remember your notes are your most important tools. Good luck!
=> END